Lyric:
[by:NickyRomero]
[00:20.84]Evolution, on a planet , I can't call mine
[00:25.67]Wasting time, in a complex universe
[00:30.69]We walk in time, piece by piece
[00:35.76]We take what we define, what's yours and what's mine
[00:41.29]Complexity, living in society
[00:47.83]Walking alone, through the sights we see
[00:53.05]We are individuals with our beliefs
[00:58.09]Hypnotized, from our degree
[01:03.29]But one day I'll fly, I'll spread my wings
[01:08.46]I'll show the whole world, what I'm meant to be
[01:13.76]I'm a human, I'm a goddamn living thing
[01:18.99]But I'm not really human, if I'm just existing
[01:24.53]Wasting my time, in a complex universe
[01:29.65]Walking in time, piece by piece
[01:34.90]Barely alive, on a planet
[01:38.74]I can't even call mine
